| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2544 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 02efa1cd-f445-5bab-89ba-76f1b7bafdc8"
